sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant D as Directory Service
    participant K as Kafka/Event Bus
    participant C as EmployeeLifecycleConsumer
    participant P as ProvisioningApplicationService
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant R as Redis
    participant A as Audit Platform

    D->>K: employee.disabled or employee.archived
    K->>C: deliver lifecycle event
    C->>P: synchronizeEmployeeStatus(event)
    P->>DB: BEGIN
    P->>DB: SELECT user FOR UPDATE by employeeRef
    P->>DB: User -> DISABLED or ARCHIVED
    P->>DB: securityVersion++
    opt archived
        P->>DB: revoke PENDING invitations
    end
    P->>DB: record event idempotency
    P->>DB: COMMIT
    P->>R: revoke all sessions and temporary challenges
    P->>A: user.status.synchronized
    C-->>K: ACK
